# act configuration — https://github.com/nektos/act
#
# Image choice: catthehacker/ubuntu:act-22.04 (~1 GB) is a good balance
# between download size and tool availability.
# Larger alternative (has more pre-installed tools, ~60 GB extracted):
#   -P ubuntu-latest=ghcr.io/catthehacker/ubuntu:full-22.04
-P ubuntu-latest=ghcr.io/catthehacker/ubuntu:act-22.04
